oc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/tshwane-university-of-technology-tut-online-application\/#Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_TUT\" title=\"Applying for Financial Assistance in TUT\">Applying for Financial Assistance in TUT<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/tshwane-university-of-technology-tut-online-application\/#Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_TUT_admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for TUT admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for TUT admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80722674\">About the Tshwane University of Technology (TUT) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80722675\"><strong>How to Apply for TUT Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80722676\">Documents Required for TUT Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80722677\">TUT Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80722678\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80722679\">Applying for Financial Assistance in TUT<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80722680\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for TUT admission 2024?<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-tshwane-university-of-technology-tut-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_Tshwane_University_of_Technology_TUT_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80722674\"><\/a>About the Tshwane University of Technology (TUT) Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the Tshwane University of Technology(TUT) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80722675\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for TUT Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4 id=\"%c2%b7-visit-here\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%C2%B7_Visit_here\"><\/span>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/ienabler.tut.ac.za\/pls\/prodi41\/gen.gw1pkg.gw1startup?x_processcode=ITS_OAP\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-tut-admission-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_TUT_Admission_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80722676\"><\/a>Documents Required for TUT Admission Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"tut-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"TUT_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80722677\"><\/a>TUT Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee of R100 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R300<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80722678\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30\u00a0September 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-tut\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_TUT\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80722679\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in TUT<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nsfas.org.za\/content\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">portal<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-tut-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_TUT_admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80722680\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for TUT admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/ienabler.tut.ac.za\/pls\/prodi41\/gen.gw1pkg.gw1startup?x_processcode=ITS_OAP\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"TUT Online Application 2024 for Admission into Tshwane University of Technology, TUT Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1144,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1143"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-jso